  "body": "Our current tests for eth1 query an actual Goerli node hosted by an external provider, which adds fragility to our test suite.\r\n\r\n- https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3993\r\n\r\nWe want to eventually not have external network dependencies in our test so:\r\n\r\n- Install some EL node locally (geth, ethereumJS)\r\n- Spin up a local testnet, and populate if necessary\r\n- Test against that local node\r\n\r\nFYI that's a significant effort, that's why it hasn't been done yet. But we do need this eventually.",
